{"tid":691651,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"「自比美斯散步踢波法」 普巴：無人可以教我怎樣踢波","createTime":"2018-06-06T03:00:05.000Z","updateTime":"2018-07-05T06:48:16.000Z","uid":5006,"like":20,"dislike":13,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"61b425da22c51224f5c91c624208b383b94b4872","tid":691651,"uid":5006,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-06T03:00:05.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://d2e7nuz2r6mjca.cloudfront.net/2018/6/1528234539_dW-1280w.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fd2e7nuz2r6mjca.cloudfront.net%2F2018%2F6%2F1528234539_dW-1280w.jpg&h=c5cdc660&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<em>法國中場保羅普巴被換出時遭主場的法國球迷柴台。不過，該名25歲球星表示，即使受到批評，他仍然不會改變自己的踢法及生活態度。</em><br />\n<br />\n對於在球場上的表現屢受批評，普巴向《法國足球》表示：「我的踢法一向都是這樣。我以往取得錦標，亦是以這種踢法去贏。<span style=\"color: red;\">你不會批評美斯在球場上踱步</span>。當他射入3球，你不會說：『噢，但他在場上踱步。』<span style=\"color: red;\">沒有人可以告訴我應該怎樣踢波</span>。<span style=\"color: red;\">我有今時今日的地位，是因為我忠於自己</span>。那是我的足球，就是如此簡單。人們有權喜歡或不喜歡。」 <br />\n<br />\n 球場以外，普巴活躍於社交網站，並不時更換髮型，令人質疑他沒有專注於足球。他在紅魔作客曼城的打吡大戰以一頭藍色頭髮現身，就遭受曼聯名宿加利尼維利批評，「如果你夠聰明的話，你不會在事情進展並不順利時，故意引起關注，但普巴不是這種人。」<br />\n<br />\n對於場外的批評，普巴指出：「我不是為了別人而活。每個人都有自己意見，我對此表示尊重。<span style=\"color: red;\">你有權去批評我，但我不會因此而改變</span>。沒有人能夠得到全世界的歡心，因為沒有東西是完美的。如有人跟我說：『我不喜歡你。』我不會感冒犯，因為那是你的權利，<span style=\"color: red;\">你真的不用喜歡我</span>。」<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n來源：<a href=\"https://www.am730.com.hk/news/share/128934\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.am730.com.hk%2Fnews%2Fshare%2F128934&d=kEmSxAroJEq%2Bdf0fzaYk5f7vEz4FU%2Bq4m%2F6ZFrWLoTs%3D&h=7f70b238\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.am730.com.hk/news/share/128934</a><br />\n==========<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 普巴踢波唔洗你教！！！<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dislike.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 唔講以為你講緊金球獎得獎感言<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/zzz.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  有無人話比我知大帝巴今年拎左幾多個冠軍<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e6f936fbb83241cb713ad80de309b7392078b386","tid":691651,"uid":96941,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-06T03:40:47.000Z","msg":"啲力架零舍多借口<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"faaa0f655957dcad860f1ee24e5dd7020796bee7","tid":691651,"uid":61015,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-06T04:49:49.000Z","msg":"睇到佢同山齊士踢波睇到想嘔血 <br />\n<br />\n成日走去持球嘅人身邊拎波踢 唔撚係走生位 扯啲空位岀黎 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"082307175ee0dff7a4e0c6c2572068f1e585ce48","tid":691651,"uid":171754,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-05T06:36:24.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"63cf10bac17caadb5347eab3398b81901254b322","tid":691651,"uid":21028,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-05T06:38:45.000Z","msg":"費夾遜唔要你真係冇撚錯"},{"pid":"5eade7bf2a85763e57e53557f064a1d06c7cab91","tid":691651,"uid":74278,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-05T06:42:39.000Z","msg":"普巴今時今日嘅地位係咪即係全球最貴水貨"},{"pid":"df7d5f71501309cbca6ef9ab09a418bc37c7a7d4","tid":691651,"uid":186181,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-05T06:48:16.000Z","msg":"咁你下場入3球黎睇下咪唔話你囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/06.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}